consequences of his sin
before I slit his throat.

753
01:16:12,129 --> 01:16:14,862
But now my vassals
are most likely dead.

754
01:16:16,962 --> 01:16:21,062
Fools rush in where
angels fear to tread.

755
01:17:05,529 --> 01:17:08,629
MICHAEL! SHOOT HIM NOW!

756
01:17:11,229 --> 01:17:15,162
What are you waiting for? Do it!

757
01:17:15,162 --> 01:17:17,029
(OS) Shoot them...

758
01:17:17,029 --> 01:17:19,729
She's dead already...

759
01:17:19,729 --> 01:17:23,262
Do it... for our Lady Sio...

760
01:17:48,962 --> 01:17:50,896
Tomoe!

761
01:18:29,896 --> 01:18:32,162
Afro Samurai...

762
01:18:34,029 --> 01:18:40,929
I knew that sooner or later
this day would come.

763
01:18:43,129 --> 01:18:46,596
I will die with you.

764
01:19:42,453 --> 01:19:44,353
What the hell?

765
01:19:44,353 --> 01:19:51,553
(long yell)
Yo Afro! Afro!!!!

766
01:20:00,586 --> 01:20:02,486
Afro! You made it!

767
01:20:02,486 --> 01:20:04,186
How'd you survive home boy?

768
01:20:04,186 --> 01:20:05,453
Tell me what I missed! Ya know,

769
01:20:05,453 --> 01:20:07,519
I got hit by a sleeping
dart. Hurt too!

770
01:20:07,519 --> 01:20:09,986
But I'm a tough, so don't worry.

771
01:20:09,986 --> 01:20:12,386
So did you whack some
crazy moth a fuckas?

772
01:20:21,653 --> 01:20:23,219
What the...?!

773
01:20:35,286 --> 01:20:37,486
Follow me, son.

774
01:20:37,486 --> 01:20:40,953
HOLY FUCK!

775
01:20:42,019 --> 01:20:46,253
Now I HAVE
officially seen it all!

776
01:21:01,553 --> 01:21:04,619
Sio... Jinno...

777
01:21:04,619 --> 01:21:08,953
Hey Afro. why you got to
walk directly into every trap?

778
01:21:08,953 --> 01:21:11,153
You stupid or what?

779
01:21:11,153 --> 01:21:13,253
Up there is the
crazy bitch who been

780
01:21:13,253 --> 01:21:14,886
pullin' the strings
this whole time

781
01:21:14,886 --> 01:21:17,019
AND your old revived robo‐pal‐‐

782
01:21:17,019 --> 01:21:19,286
who don't like your ass neither!

783
01:21:19,286 --> 01:21:21,486
On top of that,
we followin' some

784
01:21:21,486 --> 01:21:24,319
freak o nature that
you think is your dad!

785
01:21:24,319 --> 01:21:27,453
That is my real father.

786
01:21:29,919 --> 01:21:32,919
(exasperated)
Ergh! Wrong answer. That's it.

787
01:21:32,919 --> 01:21:39,153
You're an idiot. And this is as
far as I can go. See ya!

788
01:21:45,619 --> 01:21:48,319
I'm so happy you've made it.

789
01:21:48,319 --> 01:21:51,119
We've have so much to...
talk about!

790
01:21:55,586 --> 01:22:00,386
I have come for my father
and the #1 headband.

791
01:22:00,386 --> 01:22:02,486
(Dry Sarcasm)
What a surprise...

792
01:22:02,486 --> 01:22:04,319
But what can you possibly do

793
01:22:04,319 --> 01:22:09,119
with your body
so utterly destroyed?

794
01:22:24,253 --> 01:22:26,453
We're going to torture you.

795
01:22:26,453 --> 01:22:28,619
Death will come slowly.

796
01:22:45,153 --> 01:22:49,586
(groan)
Why didn't you wear
the No. 1 headband?

797
01:22:49,586 --> 01:22:54,019
I just wanted revenge...
for you.

798
01:22:54,019 --> 01:22:57,453
Whatever your reason,
one must shoulder the burden of

799
01:22:57,453 --> 01:23:01,119
destiny the instant he
puts on the headband.

800
01:23:01,119 --> 01:23:03,453
You should know that by now.

801
01:23:03,453 --> 01:23:06,219
Become the No. 1.

802
01:23:06,219 --> 01:23:10,853
You can never escape
the cycle of blood.

803
01:23:14,286 --> 01:23:17,553
The No. 1 kills or is killed.

804
01:23:17,553 --> 01:23:22,019
You don't have the luxury to
choose whose blood you spill.

805
01:23:22,019 --> 01:23:25,086
Take back your headband.

806
01:23:25,086 --> 01:23:29,319
Fear not... my son...

807
01:23:29,319 --> 01:23:32,953
Urgh... father... wait...

808
01:23:32,953 --> 01:23:34,486
Father...

809
01:24:31,886 --> 01:24:36,286
Look... Look my dear brother.

810
01:24:37,453 --> 01:24:40,219
Afro Samurai is
about to meet his end...

811
01:24:40,219 --> 01:24:42,019
Just as I planned‐‐

812
01:24:42,019 --> 01:24:45,219
at the hands of his own father!

813
01:24:48,019 --> 01:24:50,586
He will finally pay for
the pain he's caused us‐‐

814
01:24:50,586 --> 01:24:55,638
for the pain he's caused
thousands... like us!

815
01:25:41,586 --> 01:25:44,853
Jinno! Jinno!

816
01:26:07,253 --> 01:26:09,953
(excited) Kill him! Kill him!

817
01:26:09,953 --> 01:26:14,286
Once and for all! (laughter)

818
01:26:53,286 --> 01:26:55,486
(Struggling) Ahh....

819
01:26:55,486 --> 01:26:57,519
...Afro....

820
01:27:01,219 --> 01:27:04,586
(groan)

821
01:27:04,586 --> 01:27:07,219
Kill him Afro! Waste him!

822
01:27:07,219 --> 01:27:08,619
That ain't your real father!

823
01:27:08,619 --> 01:27:12,353
That's it! Finish it! Do it!

824
01:27:12,353 --> 01:27:15,919
I cannot kill my father...

825
01:27:15,919 --> 01:27:19,886
Wha... then this
is the end of Afro!

826
01:27:40,353 --> 01:27:43,053
Did you see that, Jinno?

827
01:27:43,053 --> 01:27:46,886
We did it! We finally
brought him to justice!

828
01:27:46,886 --> 01:27:51,919
And it was we...
we who killed him!!

829
01:27:51,919 --> 01:27:55,153
Look, look my dear brother!

830
01:27:57,486 --> 01:28:00,886
(realizes the change in Jinno)
Jinno? Jinno?

831
01:28:02,386 --> 01:28:04,119
(in whisper) Afro...

832
01:28:08,486 --> 01:28:11,519
Af...ro...

833
01:28:15,219 --> 01:28:19,353
Afro!!!!

834
01:28:29,119 --> 01:28:33,119
What have you done...

835
01:28:33,119 --> 01:28:36,953
What have you done to Afro?!!

836
01:28:40,086 --> 01:28:41,453
Why...?

837
01:28:42,319 --> 01:28:45,319
Jinno! Why are you
protecting Afro?!

838
01:28:45,319 --> 01:28:49,253
He's dead now! It's no use!

839
01:28:52,953 --> 01:28:58,219
Have you forgotten what
Afro did to us? To you!?!

840
01:29:19,186 --> 01:29:20,919
Jinno!

841
01:29:31,286 --> 01:29:32,453
(groan)
Afro...

842
01:29:34,253 --> 01:29:39,419
(V.O. during Sio flashback).
My... dearest... brother...

843
01:29:43,086 --> 01:29:44,453
I must...

844
01:29:45,553 --> 01:29:49,019
...protect Swordmaster's dojo...

845
01:29:50,353 --> 01:29:53,953
...must protect everyone...

846
01:29:55,886 --> 01:30:00,186
...including my brother... Afro.

847
01:31:06,219 --> 01:31:11,853
I love you my Jinno...

848
01:31:15,419 --> 01:31:17,853
My brother...

849
01:31:32,953 --> 01:31:37,319
It's been a long time,
hasn't it, Sio?

850
01:31:43,153 --> 01:31:46,553
How have you been, princess?

851
01:31:50,253 --> 01:31:52,219
Jin...no...

852
01:31:55,953 --> 01:31:57,486
(groan)

853
01:33:12,561 --> 01:33:14,928
Run, Afro! You can't win.

854
01:33:14,928 --> 01:33:18,962
I said <i>run</i>, damn it!
You can't win this one.

855
01:33:18,962 --> 01:33:22,228
He's too strong! He ain't human!

856
01:33:22,228 --> 01:33:25,628
Don't! Don't!

857
01:33:25,628 --> 01:33:28,228
Shut...

858
01:33:28,228 --> 01:33:29,595
...up.

859
01:33:30,028 --> 01:33:31,928
It'll soon be over.

860
01:33:33,095 --> 01:33:36,995
Forgive me.
But, you are not my father.

861
01:33:38,128 --> 01:33:42,462
My father died a long time ago.

862
01:33:47,095 --> 01:33:48,628
Fear not...

863
01:34:34,295 --> 01:34:35,862
Father!

864
01:34:58,328 --> 01:35:00,362
(frightened sob)

865
01:35:18,362 --> 01:35:21,495
Anytime you're ready.

866
01:35:38,362 --> 01:35:40,328
Will it ever end?

867
01:35:44,428 --> 01:35:47,895
(sigh) Guess not.

868
01:35:47,895 --> 01:35:48,795
Huh. From the look of your face,

869
01:35:48,795 --> 01:35:52,262
I'd say you had a
hell of a rough day.

870
01:35:52,262 --> 01:35:54,062
You knew this
already didn't you?

871
01:35:54,062 --> 01:35:58,328
You knew it don't
ever end once it starts.

872
01:35:58,328 --> 01:36:00,995
I <i>knew</i>, Afro Samurai.

873
01:36:00,995 --> 01:36:04,628
But, I won't say anything.
Not anymore.

874
01:36:04,628 --> 01:36:08,362
But, y'know.
Not turning your back...

875
01:36:10,128 --> 01:36:12,862
...that's the only
choice you've <i>ever</i> had.

876
01:40:56,662 --> 01:41:01,362
Been waiting a
long time for you.

